message_text: It is always important when establishing rules and routines  as a family to consider the age of each child, so you can come up with age-appropriate routines. This is most important for bedtime, time to come home/play, household chores.

condition: My children felt it was unfair that they have to follow the rule while I don’t have to follow it
condition_name: My children felt it was unfair that
message_text: We should always remember that children learn best from us. The more we follow the rules, they more they will follow the rules too. You can adjust the rule to make sure that it is realistic for everyone to follow it, considering their responsibilities (for example school or work activities).

condition: I felt uncomfortable because I feel I should be the one establishing the rule not my child or teen

message_text: When we establish rules together with our children, that helps the family to understand each other better. The rules will be more realistic and our children will be more willing and able to follow the rule.
